Race.SpecificTitle: PW Prop. (Library Tax Renewal) -- 10.90 Mills Renewal - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Grant, State of Louisiana (the "Parish") levy a special tax of ten and ninety hundredths (10.90) mills on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $534,100 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2020 and ending with the year 2029, for the purpose of maintaining, supporting and operating public libraries in the Parish?
